==English==
===Adjective===
'''fallow'''

# pale-green or light-yellow; pertaining to pale color
#(''of agricultural land'') plowed but left unseeded for more than one planting season
# [[inactive]]; [[undeveloped]]

===See also===
*[[fallow deer]]

===Noun===
'''fallow'''

# ground ploughed and harrowed but left unseeded for one year
# uncultivated land

